    "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n         <h2>AllergyIntoleranceSeverity</h2>\n         <div>\n            <p>Clinical assessment of the severity of a reaction event as a whole, potentially considering multiple different manifestations.</p> \n         </div>\n         <p>\n            <b>Copyright Statement:</b> Copyright © HL7.org 2011+\n         </p>\n         <p>This value set includes codes from the following code systems:</p>\n         <ul>\n            <li>Include these codes as defined in \n               <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/STU3/codesystem-reaction-event-severity.html\">\n                  <code>http://hl7.org/fhir/reaction-event-severity</code>\n               </a>\n               <table class=\"none\">\n                  <tr>\n                     <td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">\n                        <b>Code</b>\n                     </td>\n                     <td>\n                        <b>Display</b>\n                     </td>\n                  </tr>\n                  <tr>\n                     <td>\n                        <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/STU3/codesystem-reaction-event-severity.html#reaction-event-severity-mild\">mild</a>\n                     </td>\n                     <td>Mild</td>\n                     <td>Causes mild physiological effects.</td>\n                  </tr>\n                  <tr>\n                     <td>\n                        <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/STU3/codesystem-reaction-event-severity.html#reaction-event-severity-moderate\">moderate</a>\n                     </td>\n                     <td>Moderate</td>\n                     <td>Causes moderate physiological effects.</td>\n                  </tr>\n                  <tr>\n                     <td>\n                        <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/STU3/codesystem-reaction-event-severity.html#reaction-event-severity-severe\">severe</a>\n                     </td>\n                     <td>Severe</td>\n                     <td>Causes severe physiological effects.</td>\n                  </tr>\n               </table>\n            </li>\n         </ul>\n      </div>"
